<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Cancel Request Received</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin: 50px auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 30px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #333333;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        color: #666666;
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        text-align: justify;
      }
      .contact {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .contact a {
        color: #333333;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s ease-in-out;
      }
      .contact a:hover {
        color: #007bff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Cancel Request Received</h1>
      <p>
        Thank you for submitting your cancel request. Our team has received it
        and will review it as soon as possible. You will be notified of the
        outcome via email.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please note that the seller will review and approve or reject your
        request. If the seller approves the request, they will receive the
        products and mark them as received. The refund will then be processed
        within 7 days.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to
        <span class="contact"><a>contact our customer support team</a></span
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
